title: Be An Extravagant Giver
itunes:title: Be An Extravagant Giver
description:
You may not have exactly what someone needs today, but when you have Jesus, you always have something to give. If you want to see God do something extraordinary in your life, give what you have. He will make it into more than enough. Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
